      <lines>Let there be love shared among us,<br/>Let there be love in our eyes;<br/>May now Your love sweep this nation,<br/>Cause us, O Lord, to arise.<br/>Give us a fresh understanding<br/>Of brotherly love that is real;<br/>Let there be love shared among us,<br/>Let there be love.</lines>
